  "text": "Most importantly, the combination of our genotyping results with those from Schaefer and co-workers in a meta-analysis for the SNPs rs2891168, rs1333042, rs1333048, and rs496892 produced lower p-values as compared to the results of both the individual studies in the multiplicative model. It seems reasonable to propose a multiplicative model for the whole locus covering both LD regions, substantiating the earlier assumption of Schaefer and co-workers that the underlying genetic model might be \"somewhere between the recessive and the multiplicative one\" [CITATION_1] .",
